        <Parent_String>Eastern Subarctic Native American styles [300017461], Arctic and Subarctic Native American styles [300017443], Native North American [300017442], Native American [300017437], The Americas [300016617], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
